name: Multiple personality disorder
description: People with multiple personalities are not always wrong. Let's look at it from the positive side. He can be a super creative person, without limits on imagination. He can create stories that others may not be able to create. He doesn't limit his imagination and ways of describing or responding to things. He loves the exploration and expansion of new possibilities. If someone limits the capacity of his minds under the pretext of consistency, then it is difficult to do. Good consistency does not only maintain the visual appearance or just branding, but also the consistency to always develop new things with the mindset and visualization.
